Task: Build a Dashboard Application

    Description: Develop a dashboard application using Next.js to display various metrics and data visualizations.
    Requirements:
        Use Next.js for server-side rendering and routing.
        Implement authentication using JWT tokens or any preferred authentication method.
        Fetch data from an API (can be mock data initially).
        Display different metrics and visualizations on the dashboard, such as charts (using libraries like D3.js or Chart.js), tables, and cards.
        Ensure responsiveness for different screen sizes.
        Implement client-side routing to navigate between different sections of the dashboard.
        Write clean and maintainable code with proper error handling and validation.
    Bonus:
        
        Add user settings to customize the dashboard layout or theme.
        Optimize performance by lazy-loading components or implementing server-side caching strategies.
